  "3010210": {
    "name": "幸存者救赎",
    "steam_appid": 3010210,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《幸存者：救赎》将经典 RPG 进程与类 Roguelike 幸存者融合在一起，从《暗黑破坏神》和《流放之路》等经典游戏中汲取灵感。升级、收集宝石以提高您的属性，并变得更强大以应对不断升级的挑战。救赎之旅正在等着您！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗系统围绕两个核心元素设计：角色的自动攻击和从技能卡中选择的技能，以及宠物的伤害。这款游戏的难度可不是开玩笑的——每场战斗都是对你的技能和策略的真正考验！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/10e2ab61e6af16063a3018aab5c30b53.poster.avif?t=1743955935\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/10e2ab61e6af16063a3018aab5c30b53.webm?t=1743955935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/10e2ab61e6af16063a3018aab5c30b53.mp4?t=1743955935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装备强化系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的游戏融合了传统的 RPG 进阶元素。这是用于升级装备和提升角色基本属性的装备强化系统。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/e183f40413376344ef1666e881b58059.poster.avif?t=1743955935\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/e183f40413376344ef1666e881b58059.webm?t=1743955935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/e183f40413376344ef1666e881b58059.mp4?t=1743955935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>宠物系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了角色自身的攻击和技能外，宠物还扮演着下一个关键角色。使用符文增强宝石来增强宠物。它们的攻击潜力非常大，因此一定要充分利用它们，以最大限度地提高战斗中的伤害！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/1a38bdb17f63ba849c7e6577453c4c47.poster.avif?t=1743955935\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/1a38bdb17f63ba849c7e6577453c4c47.webm?t=1743955935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/1a38bdb17f63ba849c7e6577453c4c47.mp4?t=1743955935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>符文系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >符文系统是补充装备升级的附加属性增强系统。符文可增强攻击、防御等核心属性。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/dbe89da6ae970f83f7229cdfe071491f.poster.avif?t=1743955935\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/dbe89da6ae970f83f7229cdfe071491f.webm?t=1743955935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/dbe89da6ae970f83f7229cdfe071491f.mp4?t=1743955935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>卡牌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次游戏期间，你都可以通过击败敌人并升级来获得卡牌。卡牌分为三种类型：属性卡、技能卡和物品卡。请记住，卡牌效果仅适用于当前游戏会话。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/2967b311cceaa1e59d639568c202359e.poster.avif?t=1743955935\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/2967b311cceaa1e59d639568c202359e.webm?t=1743955935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/2967b311cceaa1e59d639568c202359e.mp4?t=1743955935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宝箱</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败怪物可掉落宝箱，宝箱内有各类强化石，是一个非常不错的获取资源方式，只不过比较靠运气，所以还是尽量多多的获取宝箱吧<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/9769b162a265d0a7c68167b99459e98a.poster.avif?t=1743955935\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/9769b162a265d0a7c68167b99459e98a.webm?t=1743955935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/9769b162a265d0a7c68167b99459e98a.mp4?t=1743955935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >怪物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中有各种小型怪物，但要特别注意带有红色半径指示器的大型敌人。如果你发现自己被太多敌人压倒，你可以利用这些爆炸怪物来获得优势。它们可以在靠近敌人时引爆，帮助清除大群敌人。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/4e8447a276bebb2140a3914232835574.poster.avif?t=1743955935\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/4e8447a276bebb2140a3914232835574.webm?t=1743955935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/4e8447a276bebb2140a3914232835574.mp4?t=1743955935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Boss</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个级别都有两个 Boss，一个小 Boss 和一个大 Boss。小 Boss 的攻击相当容易躲避，但大 Boss 的攻击范围更大，而且攻击力惊人！保持警惕，掌握躲避技巧，因为一个错误的举动可能会让你失去一切！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/6ce5d1eead2972eed51bbffa97ec064e.poster.avif?t=1743955935\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/6ce5d1eead2972eed51bbffa97ec064e.webm?t=1743955935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010210/extras/6ce5d1eead2972eed51bbffa97ec064e.mp4?t=1743955935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>地图</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏有四个难度等级，每个等级有六个独特级别，总共有 24 张令人兴奋的地图可供探索。</p>",
